========================
Shopinvader Mailjet
========================

This module use mailjet for sending email and doing the templating with mailjet
As version 10 of odoo seem to be better in email templating, this module maybe will be drop in 10

Bug Tracker
===========

Bugs are tracked on `GitHub Issues
<https://github.com/akretion/odoo-shopinvader/issues>`_. In case of trouble, please
check there if your issue has already been reported. If you spotted it first,
help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed feedback.

